{"tid":1299700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有冇諗過香港係需要林奠月娥？","createTime":"2019-07-09T06:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T06:34:31.000Z","uid":58104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9f3708bee8241827f69584f79257c2f3bb4b007d","tid":1299700,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"其實係林奠主動破左共產黨兩個大局<br />\n1. 溫水煮蛙<br />\n2. 換血 (150)<br />\n<br />\n好多香港人其實係比林奠喚醒左對共產黨既恐惧！<br />\n<br />\n講真呢一刻我唔會想佢下台，<br />\n希望佢頂得住共產黨既壓力，<br />\n甚至希望佢做多d野激化事件。<br />\n<br />\n希望香港人撐住！<br />\n全民皆兵，港獨可期！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ba46ef7aebad65fab73d7184db7d86e7758f8f","tid":1299700,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"長痛，不如短痛。"},{"pid":"b831f7463ce7ae77cbc522ce819ea1da5eea2b2d","tid":1299700,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"#weconnect<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931aa25bc5f627087a67708f644e4d428f07d2f3","tid":1299700,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b831f7463ce7ae77cbc522ce819ea1da5eea2b2d","tid":1299700,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"#weconnect<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:34:31.000Z","msg":"connect埋林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}